Text.Value: We prepare an army of our own. The Steel Watch will be mobilised.
Next, we identify all enemies within our walls and within our ranks.
Let the people rejoice: in Archduke Gortash's hands, they are safe.
And if the Steel Watch can't protect us? What then?
Under Gortash, the two will conquer the cult army and preserve our city and our heritage.
We restore the Steel Watch to capacity and mobilise it.
The people demand it. Is a Baldurian truly free when he fears for his future?
